snippet.title: Huntr/x - GOLDEN (Epic Metal Cover by SIEG)
snippet.description:
Hello everyone,

It's been a while since my last update. I promised to work consistently on music this year, but unexpected challenges came up that delayed my work, and I apologize for keeping you waiting.

I know many creators follow trends and put out content quickly, but that's never been my approach. I work with different standards and timelines than other YouTubers.

Usually I work as part of a band with talented musicians, but this time circumstances led me to work solo with some technical assistance. Despite everything, I couldn't leave my fans waiting any longer, so I managed to complete this track during a brief creative break from my busy schedule.
Today I'm presenting a metal cover of "Golden" by Huntr/x, the virtual band from K-Pop Demon Hunters series. I've reimagined the original with powerful metal elements while preserving its core essence.

I was able to create the backing track with modern production tools, which I then enhanced with my vocals and video editing. Though this was a solo project, I put my heart into it with the desire to share something special with all of you.

Thank you for your continued support, and I promise more music is coming your way.

Credits:
Siegfried Song (SoniKhaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing & Arrangement
Original Song: Huntr/x - Golden (from K-Pop Demon Hunters)

Please support with likes, subscriptions, and comments!
What's your favorite part of this metal version? Let me know!

#HuntrX #Golden #MetalCover #KpopDemonHunters #MetalMusic #CoverSong #Siegfried #SoniKhaos
